title: It Seems That I’ve Slipped Into a Different World. Also, My Gender Has Changed. - Novel Updates
genre: Comedy   Fantasy   Gender Bender   Mystery   Romance   Slice of Life   Supernatural
tags: Doting Parents   Engagement   Female Protagonist   Magic   Male to Female   Nobles   Returning from Another World   Sister Complex   Transmigration   Transported to Another World   Younger Brothers
author: Yamabuki Yumi   山吹弓美
description: I, Seiren Shikino grew up in an orphanage. On the day of my high school graduation, I somehow got transported to another world, and turned into a girl as well. ……Eh, this isn’t my original world and gender, right!? It seems that I’m now Seiren, the daughter of a noble from another world. This is a light hearted story about family and romance.>
